        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 to 45 years old (to exclude the effect of age on glucose tolerance);

          -  BMI between 20 and 25 kg/m2 (to exclude individuals that are likely to have impaired
             insulin response);

          -  Normal fasting glucose;

          -  Stable weight for three months before participation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI >25kg/m2;

          -  Fasting glucose â‰¥126 mg/dl

          -  Shift work or disordered sleep (to exclude individuals with alterations in the
             hypothalamus-adrenergic axis);

          -  Any diseases;

          -  Use of any medication regularly (including over-the-counter);

          -  Previous exposure to GCs (within the last year);

          -  Pregnancy
